rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, you heard of a Torigonda?

rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, it's the instrument
I'm playing right now.

rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm up every night practicing, but
I'm still not good enough.

rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Us Gulan love music, after all.
I won't be a proper adult until I can
pull off a flawless performance!
